high_descs: Move to the arm chair closet to the cat tree.
Pick up a watch from the arm chair.
Move around to the front of the arm chair.
Place the watch inside the box on the arm chair.
Pick up the box from the arm chair.
Move to the coffee table in front of the couch.
Place the box on the coffee table.
anns.task_desc: Put a box with a watch inside it on the coffee table.

high_descs: Turn around and take a step forward, then turn right and walk up to the wall, turn right again to face the red chair.
Pick up the watch that is closest to you off of the seat of the red chair.
Turn right and walk around to the front of the red chair that you picked the watch up off of.
Put the watch into the cardboard box that is on the seat of the red chair.
Pick up the cardboard box with the watch in it.
Turn right and begin walking across the room, then hang a right and walk up to the wooden coffee table.
Place the cardboard box with the watch inside onto the coffee table to the right of the book.
anns.task_desc: Put a cardboard box with a watch inside on a coffee table.

high_descs: Turn around and get between the cat tree and red chair, standing next to the wall on your left and the right arm of the red chair in front of you.
Pick up the watch from off the chair that is on the right hand side closer to you.
Walk around the red chair nearest the cat tree to stand in front of it.
Put the watch into the white box that is on the red chair.
Pick up the white box with the watch in it.
Turn around and walk to the low wooden coffee table that is in front of the red sofa, sitting on the rug.
Put the white box on the coffee table, in between a book and a watch.
anns.task_desc: Put a white box with one watch in it on the coffee table.

high_descs: Walk to the left side of the pink chair with two watches on it.
Pick up the watch closest to the edge from the pink chair.
Walk to the front of the pink chair with a box on it.
Place the watch in the box.
Pick up the box from the pink chair.
Turn around and walk to the wooden table with a book on it.
Place the box next to the book on the wooden table.
anns.task_desc: Place a box with a watch in it next to the book on the wooden table.
